description.en: YouLive's vision is to build the truly decentralized live social platform through blockchain technology to enable real-time content sharing, social networking and circle building through community-based autonomy through subversive value recognition and value Allocation mechanism, so that all participants in the ecology can be obtained directly from the other side of the value of affirmation.
